        P["Write around diagram:\nHook · thesis · proof · CTA"]
        Q{"Clear and scannable?"}
        R["Ship post + code + image set 🚀"]
        W["Watch comments for confusion"]
  end
    S(("Spark ✨")) --> T["👀 Notice text fatigue"]
